Class ByteBufHttpData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linecorp.armeria.common.AbstractHttpData
      • com.linecorp.armeria.unsafe.ByteBufHttpData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpData, HttpObject, ByteBufHolder, ReferenceCounted
    public class ByteBufHttpData
extends AbstractHttpData
implements ByteBufHolder
    A HttpData that is backed by a ByteBuf for optimizing certain internal use cases. Not for general use.
